HEADWORD: Abeam
<hw>A*beam"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>a-</ets> + <ets>beam</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>On the
beam, that is, on a line which forms a right angle with the ship's keel;
opposite to the center of the ship's side.</def>⟦br⟧
